upcoming.name: GDG DevFest Kharkiv 2019
upcoming.description:
GDG DevFest (or Developer Festival) is a series of events held by Google Development Group worldwide. Now in Kharkiv!

For students, young IT specialists, startup creators, and for everyone who is inspired by information technology

When: November 23
Duration: 9:00 -18:00 (lunch and coffee break included).
Format: 2 streams, 5 sessions each. Expert panel and ¬´round-tables¬ª.

Conference streams:

‚Ä¢ Cloud, Google Cloud Platform
‚Ä¢ Machine Learning/TensorFlow
‚Ä¢ IoT
‚Ä¢ VR, Daydream
‚Ä¢ Web Technologies
‚Ä¢ Soft Skills

Notes:

‚Ä¢ In 2019, that is the only DevFest held by Google Development Group in Ukraine.
‚Ä¢ Lectures by hands-on experts (IT-company owners, startup creators) and theorists (university professors).
‚Ä¢ Round table discussions with the speakers after their presentations (for networking and exchanging experience).

2019 Kharkiv Conference Highlights:

‚Ä¢ 10+ speakers (University professors and hands-on experts).
‚Ä¢ 10 sessions (Relevant topics in the IT-sphere).
‚Ä¢ 200 attendees (IT-specialists, students, startups creators)

Improve your professional skills with the best IT experts in Ukraine

To get a ticket to GDG DevFest Kharkiv 2019 support Kharkiv Regional Specialized Child Care Center ‚Ññ1 ¬´Hippokrat¬ª.

First, transfer 300 UAH or more to the center's account http://hippocrat.org.ua/ (button at the bottom of the site)

Then fill out the form to get registered and send us a screenshot of your receipt https://forms.gle/9MuziB2H5fBBdrGd8

Want to know more? Check it http://devfest2019.gdg-cloud.kharkiv.ua/
